-29T23:39:23.000Z","msg":"我想問如果成日好想死，覺得自己冇咩價值。成日無啦啦喊，要係個被竇到笠住自己攬實自己一兩個鐘都未平伏到，有時會無啦啦手震，個心成日un住咁，已經兩個星期都係咁，想開心又開心唔到，無力去處理其他事，有活動都唔想去，我係咪應該要去睇下精神科？<br />\n如果要，睇邊個比較好？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T07:34:33.000Z","msg":"要 中左幾個抑鬱徵狀<br />\n可以用心理治療/睇精神科處理<br />\n經濟許可就私家醫生 唔許可就拿拿林去住個區既醫院排期"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"我以前係中學果時爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果時個社工都叫有heart立即陪我去醫院睇急症話我想自殺(事實上果時真係崩潰咁)  立即收左我入院 出院無幾耐兩個星期左右就排到見精神科 不過而家應該無呢招可以用"},{"pid":"7d7f280642d77dc463d4f9e60970006a42a2c6ee","tid":2345602,"uid":286206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f20e1b79ebc8706888ceb56a5b53bdeeb24bf6ca","tid":2345602,"uid":367551,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T03:23:13.000Z","msg":"藥物令我嘅大腦好似諗唔到負面野 但係我又唔係開心 呢樣野令我更加痛苦 之前有啲負面想法 都可以叫做有野陪住我 而家更顯孤獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"個情緒好似一條直線咁無上無落 明既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74593af4245ed75b6f7083e384062910228ccd1","tid":2345602,"uid":61976,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:40:49.000Z","msg":"我都想知 以前最鍾意睇書睇戲<br />\n而家睇幾頁頂唔順 睇幾分鐘都冇耐性<br />\n打機都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1547e3107a7d7bc7db754397417a5512cce7b094","tid":2345602,"uid":324123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T22:26:12.000Z","msg":"而家有無返工"},{"pid":"0c0292742ad6ce32ff2e68c17c4cf3e90d02c6ea","tid":2345602,"uid":241817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T22:52:35.000Z","msg":"嘗試接受自己係自己"},{"pid":"227ab744a45790d34baf2ebd2974cac823fc1694","tid":2345602,"uid":216704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T23:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc42ed6e7a22441a8d1ac2a6350f31df5a1ea769","tid":2345602,"uid":164838,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"雖然我冇睇醫生確診我抑鬱<br />\n早期返工壓力大<br />\n搞到我個人長期好down <br />\n對所有嘢都失去興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQuit 了"},{"pid":"fad2819fbd24c53b9c14c0d357e0356666636b79","tid":2345602,"uid":118922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T00:23:43.000Z","msg":"做運動 做gym 食朱古力 增加快樂因子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做gym其實都幾好 努力完 痛苦完 會有效果 會有成就感 而且人係世上就係需要肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要明白抑鬱都市病黎 10個有8個都有 唔係你諗埋一邊造成 可能係你大腦缺少樣物質 而呢點你控制唔到 但可能改善既"},{"pid":"3d22bf7f3a53254260de9ec27df8b53034111fbd","tid":2345602,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"睇西醫食焦慮藥副作用好大又撚貴<br />\n我食左4日已經唔撚食<br />\n食左仲衰過唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食中藥效果又唔明顯但冇明顯副作用<br />\n但都唔知食到幾時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a61a3a514cf869c754cc22800e3c521959c5f3","tid":2345602,"uid":50404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"我都係對所有事情都失去哂興趣噤，覺得對所有情感、事物都好麻木；之前讀書時已經係噤，但未有噤嚴重，出咗黎做嘢之後就更加嚴重。有時同朋友一齊時都有少少開心既感覺，但有時成班朋友覺得好好笑嘅片or事我都唔係好笑得出，成日懷疑自己係咪以後都會感覺唔到「快樂、開心」既情感。<br />\n有時覺得自己對所有嘢都冇哂感覺好辛苦，好似完全同情感隔絕咗噤，覺得自己好似同全世界、朋友之間有好大既距離感，朋友又冇義務去開解你or了解你點解噤沉成個人，所以自己會屈住屈住噤，喺朋友面前都有時係迫自己開心啲、正能量啲。<br />\n<br />\n我既情況又未去到覺得好撚sad嘅感覺（有時會有啲傷感），所以唔知自己應唔應該睇醫生。<br />\n<br />\n以前有做gym，覺得嗰陣個人係有比較開心。武漢肺炎好啲之後想試下返返去做gym，希望會好少少。<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c111d1a99f96f49e5168550e946ab3a53f07e1","tid":2345602,"uid":341236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d22bf7f3a53254260de9ec27df8b53034111fbd","tid":2345602,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"睇西醫食焦慮藥副作用好大又撚貴<br />\n我食左4日已經唔撚食<br />\n食左仲衰過唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食中藥效果又唔明顯但冇明顯副作用<br />\n但都唔知食到幾時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"同醫生講個副作用好大<br />\n轉藥喇<br />\n轉啱藥會冇乜副作用"},{"pid":"f538b163311b3baffddfcf7d3874ccc79d4783de","tid":2345602,"uid":346854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"做尖"},{"pid":"49f7f400f30c16254835e0b2edf7c1bc45860d40","tid":2345602,"uid":119512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3438e3b48853587eb3c933d34970cc3506b2a5","tid":2345602,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c111d1a99f96f49e5168550e946ab3a53f07e1","tid":2345602,"uid":341236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d22bf7f3a53254260de9ec27df8b53034111fbd","tid":2345602,"uid":194876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:02:17.000Z","msg":"睇西醫食焦慮藥副作用好大又撚貴<br />\n我食左4日已經唔撚食<br />\n食左仲衰過唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食中藥效果又唔明顯但冇明顯副作用<br />\n但都唔知食到幾時<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"同醫生講個副作用好大<br />\n轉藥喇<br />\n轉啱藥會冇乜副作用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"我睇過2次西醫<br />\n1次副作用大<br />\n1次毫無作用<br />\n已放棄"}]}